Protocol
------------------------------------------------------------------------

BeHappy Desktop communicates using the MVSy 1.0 protocol, an
independently developed protocol that shares some structural similarity
with MTProto 2.0 but is not interoperable with Telegram servers.

The MVSy 1.0 specification and reference implementation are available at:

    https://github.com/behappy-app/bh-mvsy

